title: Cute Prairie Village 2bd/1 bath $975  Available Sept. 1st
map_address: 800 Meadow Lake Place near County Rd 10
posting_body: ['Voted #1 Apartment Community in Carver County.', ' You will love our 2 bd/1bath Prairie Village unit is very spacious with 770 sq ft!  Bedrooms are on opposite ends of the apartment to give you privacy.', ' The master bedroom features a nice walk in closet.', ' The kitchen has plenty of cabinets, as well as a dishwasher.', ' Every unit has their own balcony or patio, so you can relax outside on all those nice days!', ' Each building has an on-site laundry room.', ' Single stall garages are also available so you can protect your vehicle from the weather.', ' These rent for $75.00 per month.', ' We also have a playground on-site for your children.', ' Like to take walks?', ' We have a walking path next to our property.', ' Also, Safari Island is a few blocks away.', ' This features an indoor pool, basketball courts, exercise equipment, etc.', ' Our property is located next to Hwy 5, and provides an easy commute to the cities.', ' Call us today to schedule a showing, and find out about our move in special!']
